) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]

    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]

) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[ProductId], [t].[BrandId], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductImage], [t].[ProductName], [t].[ProductStatusId], [t].[Quantity], [t].[StoreId], [t].[SubCategoryId], [p0].[ProductDetailId], [p0].[Attribute], [p0].[ProductId], [p0].[Value], [i].[ImageId], [i].[ImageName], [i].[ProductId], [i].[StoredImage]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[ProductId], [p].[BrandId], [p].[CategoryId], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductImage], [p].[ProductName], [p].[ProductStatusId], [p].[Quantity], [p].[StoreId], [p].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    WHERE [p].[ProductId] = @__productId_0
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [ProductDetails] AS [p0] ON [t].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [Images] AS [i] ON [t].[ProductId] = [i].[ProductId]

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE ([o].[OrderId] = [o0].[OrderId]) AND (([p].[ProductId] IS NOT NULL) AND ([p].[StoreId] = @__storeId_0)))
ORDER BY [o].[OrderId], [t].[OrderItemId]

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p].[ProductId]
    WHERE ([o].[OrderId] = [o0].[OrderId]) AND (([p].[ProductId] IS NOT NULL) AND ([p].[StoreId] = @__storeId_0)))

    SELECT [o1].[OrderItemId], [o1].[OrderId], [o1].[ProductId], [o1].[Quantity], [p0].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[BrandId], [p0].[CategoryId], [p0].[Price], [p0].[ProductImage], [p0].[ProductName], [p0].[ProductStatusId], [p0].[Quantity] AS [Quantity0], [p0].[StoreId], [p0].[SubCategoryId]
    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o1]
    LEFT JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o1].[ProductId] = [p0].[ProductId]
) AS [t] ON [o].[OrderId] = [t].[OrderId]

    FROM [OrderItems] AS [o0]
